    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 (not assessed) consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met at all five operating points, supporting the regulatory submission claim.",
